Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.64,0:24:06.47,yugao,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝 不過不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.68,0:24:08.00,yugao,NTP,0,0,0,,下回 野良神
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.03,0:24:09.17,yugao,NTP,0,0,0,,招致而來的災禍
